headline: Kimberly-Clark: Weak Growth Performance Continues To Be A Major Concern (Rating Upgrade)
summary: KMB's Q4 sales fell 0.8% y/y, with organic sales growth at 2.3%, but only 0.7% excluding hyperinflationary markets. Explore more details here.
